ction and not on the temperature, and\ntherefore, the dense gas fraction increases with the mass of GMCs, at least in\nthe GMCs with a low star-forming activity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Oct 2012 16:46:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-11"}
