ollows the\nabundances of the neighboring elements palladium and silver. We identify\nseveral sources of systematic uncertainty that must be considered when\ncomparing these abundances with theoretical predictions. We also present new\nisotope shift and hyperfine structure component patterns for Lu II and Pb I\nlines of astrophysical interest.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Oct 2012 21:35:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-11"}
